    "Metadata": {
        "Title": "Berlin Ghoul",
        "Description": "Helena Senft, a former employee for the bio-tech corporation Ether, was a brilliant geneticist known for her pioneering work in human augmentation. Her research and fast paced approach earned her the nickname &apos;The Bunny&apos;. After her time at Ether, she faked her death to escape their control and began selling secrets on the black market. She is ironically recognizable by the same bunny mask she uses to hide her identity. You will need to eliminate her hired guns as well. Good hunting, 47.\r\rThis contract was created by a member of the HITMAN community known as GlitchFood.",
